    "",
    "Schema:",
    "  <asns_code>: {",
    "    'ficd_param':       string  | null   FICD long-format ingredient column key",
    "    'unit_factor':      number  default 1.0  multiplier applied to ASNS *spec value*",
    "                                              so it lives in FICD's units; LP coefficients",
    "                                              come unchanged from FICD",
    "    'ficd_param_pelleted':  optional      use this when processing_method='pelleted'",
    "    'ficd_param_extruded':  optional      use this when processing_method='extruded'",
    "    'spec_label':       human-readable",
    "    'unit_asns':        ASNS unit (informational)",
    "    'unit_ficd':        FICD unit (informational)",
    "    'note':             freeform",
    "  }",
    "",
    "When ficd_param is null, the spec is unmappable in MVP and is dropped with a warning.",
    "Ratio constraints (e.g., ADPXF09 DP/DE) carry _ratio_numer / _ratio_denom keys instead."
